<trans-unit id='045'  resname='IDS_LEVEL1_BEGIN'><source>AH, WELCOME YOUNG PERRY THE REBEL-PUS!\nMEET MY GIANT FLYING AND ABSOLUTELY ORIGINAL NORMTROOPER-INATOR, COMPLETE WITH ANTI-MAGNET-ANTENNAE V2.0!</source></trans-unit>
