<trans-unit id='048'  resname='IDS_LEVEL2_BEGIN'><source>WE MEET AGAIN, PERRY THE REBEL-PUS!\nTHE CIRCLE IS NOW COMPLETE.</source></trans-unit>
<trans-unit id='049'  resname='IDS_LEVEL2_BEGIN2'><source>WHAT'S THAT? YOU WANT TO KNOW ABOUT MY SECRET PROJECT?\nYOU'LL NEVER GUESS! HA HA HA!</source></trans-unit>
<trans-unit id='050'  resname='IDS_LEVEL2_END'><source>OKAY, OKAY... I'M WORKING ON AN EVIL SITH-INATOR.\nBUT YOU'LL NEVER STOP ME! HA HA HA HAAAA!</source></trans-unit>
<trans-unit id='051'  resname='IDS_LEVEL3_BEGIN'><source>WHAAAT? PERRY THE REBEL-PUS AGAIN?!\nCAN'T YOU JUST LEAVE ME TO MY PLANS OF EVIL GALACTIC DOMINATION?</source></trans-unit>
<trans-unit id='052'  resname='IDS_LEVEL3_BEGIN2'><source>NO? THEN YOU'LL JUST HAVE TO FACE OFF AGAINST MY FULLY ARMED AND OPERATIONAL SUPER NORMTROOPER V3.0!</source></trans-unit>
<trans-unit id='053'  resname='IDS_LEVEL3_END'><source>CURSE YOU PERRY THE REBEL-PUS!\nI'LL GET YOU IN THE NEXT TRILOGY!</source></trans-unit>
