<trans-unit id='055'  resname='IDS_LEVEL_SUMMARY1'><source>THE EMPIRE HAS BUILT A HUGE BATTLE STATION:\nTHE DEATH STAR!\nINFILTRATE IT AND FIND OUR LOST AGENTS!</source></trans-unit>
<trans-unit id='056'  resname='IDS_LEVEL_SUMMARY2'><source>DARTHENSHMIRTZ IS WORKING ON A NEW INATOR. RESCUE MORE LOST AGENTS AND TRY TO UNCOVER WHAT IT IS!</source></trans-unit>
